---
// Newsletter Component - Reutilizable en todas las páginas
---

<section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden bg-primary dark:bg-background-dark">
  <svg class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-10 pointer-events-none" preserveAspectRatio="none" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
    <path d="M0 50 Q 25 30 50 50 T 100 50 V 100 H 0 Z" fill="white"></path>
  </svg>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center">
    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-7xl md:text-8xl text-secondary mb-6 block mx-auto animate-bounce">mark_email_unread</span>
    <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white mb-6 leading-tight">Comienza tu viaje hacia una<br/> <span class="text-secondary italic">Vida Consciente</span></h2>
    <p class="text-gray-200 font-light text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Suscríbete para recibir meditaciones gratuitas, novedades sobre talleres y capítulos exclusivos de mi nuevo libro.
    </p>
    
    <!-- Gift Banner -->
    <div class="bg-secondary/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-secondary/30 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-secondary">redeem</span>
        <span class="text-secondary font-bold">REGALO EXCLUSIVO</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-white font-display text-xl mb-1">Descarga Gratis: 30 Tips de Vida</p>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Al suscribirte recibirás instantáneamente este PDF con consejos prácticos para vivir con mayor consciencia.</p>
    </div>
    
    <form action="https://formsubmit.co/adriana@adricrisrueda.com" method="POST" class="flex flex-col gap-4 justify-center max-w-lg mx-auto relative">
      <!-- Configuración Formsubmit -->
      <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://adricrisrueda.com/gracias">
      <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Nueva suscripción a Vida Consciente">
      <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false">
      <input type="hidden" name="_template" value="table">
      
      <input 
        type="text" 
        name="nombre"
        placeholder="Tu nombre" 
        class="w-full px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-gray-900 bg-surface-light focus:ring-2 focus:ring-secondary focus:outline-none border-none shadow-xl font-light placeholder-gray-400"
        required
      />
      <input 
        type="email" 
        name="email"
        placeholder="Tu correo electrónico" 
        class="w-full px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-gray-900 bg-surface-light focus:ring-2 focus:ring-secondary focus:outline-none border-none shadow-xl font-light placeholder-gray-400"
        required
      />
      <label class="flex items-start gap-3 text-left cursor-pointer">
        <input type="checkbox" required class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded border-gray-300 text-secondary focus:ring-secondary flex-shrink-0">
        <span class="text-sm text-white/80">
          Acepto el tratamiento de mis datos personales según la <a href="/privacidad" class="underline hover:text-secondary transition-colors">Política de Privacidad</a>
        </span>
      </label>
      <button 
        type="submit"
        class="bg-secondary text-primary font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-primary transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-secondary/30 whitespace-nowrap tracking-wide mt-2 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
      >
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">mail</span>
        SUSCRIBIRME Y RECIBIR MI PDF
      </button>
    </form>
    <p class="text-xs text-white/40 mt-6 font-light">Unimos fuerzas con tu privacidad. Sin spam, solo esencia.</p>
  </div>
</section>
